<div class='commentbox'>
Ran Valley Falls this afternoon, and had a blast. Good, clean fun. We spoke to the ranger about<br/>
running the whole section, but apparently the take out is completely INACCESSIBLE. The road to the<br/>
take out was washed out and has not been repaired. just fyi. </div>
</td>
